Linux
	Execute the following commands:
	$ TEXMF=`kpsewhich -var-value TEXMFHOME`
	$ mkdir -p $TEXMF/tex/latex/beamer/AGH
	$ cp *.sty $TEXMF/tex/latex/beamer/AGH
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Windows
	Copy *.sty to texmf tree - see: http://tex.stackexchange.com/questions/12701/where-is-texmf-on-a-windows-install
